## RAP Pipeline & Dashboards

### Quick orientation

| What | Where |
|---|---|
| Project root | `~/dev/projects/liferay-release-analytics/` |
| DB | PostgreSQL `release_analytics` (local) |
| Pipeline entry | `bash run_pipeline.sh` |
| Export script | `utils/export_looker.R` (use v2 — see below) |
| Data destination | Google Sheets → Looker Studio |
| Two dashboards | Situation Deck (S-files) · Landscape Report (L-files) |

### Architecture

```
Jira (LPP/LPD/Stories) ──┐
Testray                  ──┤
lizard (CCN/NLOC)        ──┤──► PostgreSQL ──► export_looker.R ──► Google Sheets ──► Looker Studio
git churn CSVs           ──┤
breaking changes         ──┘
feature flags            ──► apply_feature_flag_dampening.R

liferay-portal checkout ──► evaluate_pr.sh ──► branch risk score (standalone)
```

### Key tables

| Table | Grain | Key fields |
|---|---|---|
| `dim_release` | 1 per release | `release_label`, `release_date`, `is_major_release`, `is_lts`, `months_in_field`, `release_status` |
| `dim_component` | 1 per component | 240 components, 15 teams |
| `dim_module_component_map` | module → component | join key = `module_path` → `dim_module.module_path_full` |
| `dim_module` | 1 per module | `module_path_full`, `module_path_category` |
| `fact_forecast_input` | component × quarter | `churn_count`, `lpp_actual`, `lpd_actual`, `story_count`, `breaking_count`, `is_forecast_row`, `is_feature_flagged`, `churn_dampening_factor` |
| `fact_file_complexity` | file (lizard snapshot) | `avg_ccn`, `max_ccn`, `avg_nloc`, `avg_ccn_java`, `avg_ccn_frontend`, `language_mix` |
| `fact_test_quality` | test case | `routine_id` is key join field |
| `fact_triage_results` | PR × case | triage pipeline output: `BUG / NEEDS_REVIEW / FALSE_POSITIVE` |
| `stg_lizard_raw` | function-level staging | aggregated → `fact_file_complexity` |

**Retired:** `fact_release_complexity` (SonarQube era)

### Composite risk scores

**Dashboard forecast (component × quarter):**
- `lpp_hist_score` = 60% historical bug average + 40% churn signal, normalized 0–100
- `lpd_pred` = Random Forest regression; requires `months_in_field >= 9`
- `risk_score` = `(lpp_hist_score + lpd_pct) / 2`, range 0–100
- `overall_risk` tier: Very High / High / Medium / Low / Very Low

**PR Risk Scoring Engine (standalone):**

| Signal | Weight |
|---|---|
| Code complexity (`max_ccn`) | 28% |
| Churn | 25% |
| Defects | 20% |
| Test coverage | 15% |
| Dependencies | 12% |

- `max_ccn` p95 denominator = **16 (fixed)** — CCN capped at 100 before aggregation
- Rationale in `scoring_normalization` — do not recalibrate silently

### Testray routine IDs — never conflate

| Signal | Routine ID | Cadence |
|---|---|---|
| Acceptance | 590307 | Daily |
| Release | 82964 | Pre-ship |

### Dashboard file map

**Situation Deck (S-files):** P1 Bug Forecast, P2 Team Release Story, P3 Risk Heat Map, P4 Churn Trends, P5 Team Scorecard, P6 Model Notes

**Landscape Report (L-files):** P1 Severity Distribution, P2 Bug Discovery Timing, P3 Language Blind Spots, P4 Complexity & Tech Debt, P5 Topic Analysis (filter by `period`, not `year`)

### Team Release Story layout (single-page one-pager)

| Row | Content |
|---|---|
| 1 – Headline Bar | avg_risk_score, risk tier, status |
| 2 – Where You Stand | Landscape / Situation / Scorecard panels |
| 3 – The Story | S01 risk heat map table |
| 4 – Stakes/Forecast | lpp_hist_score vs lpd_pred with actuals |

### Current status / known broken (April 2026)

- Use `export_looker_v2.R` — do not run old `export_looker.R`
- `is_forecast_row` = FALSE for all rows — fix pending in `transform_forecast_input.R`
- Testray signals showing 0 — routine ID verification pending
- U148 missing from `releases.yml` — re-run `sync_releases.R`
- 2026.Q1 churn = 0 — re-run post-release
- `churn_dampening_factor` stored but not consumed yet

⚠️ **Do not re-run `export_looker.R` until upstream fixes are in place.**

