## Testray Triage Pipeline

### What it is

Full bug triage pipeline for Testray Routine 82964 (Release). Identifies PASSED→FAILED regressions, filters git diffs to relevant files, classifies cases as `BUG / NEEDS_REVIEW / FALSE_POSITIVE`.

### Key components

| Component | Purpose |
|---|---|
| SQL queries | Identify PASSED→FAILED regressions |
| `extract_relevant_hunks.py` | Filters git diff to relevant files using `--exact` path matching |
| Claude (LLM layer) | Classifies each case across batches |
| `fact_triage_results` | Upsert destination |

### Path matching note

`extract_relevant_hunks.py` splits on ` / ` (with whitespace) to avoid over-matching. Use `--exact` flag. The 595k-line full diff was filtered to 56 files / ~4,755 lines for routine 82964.

### Long-term goal

Feed `fact_triage_results` classifications into `pr_outcomes` as labeled training data for an NN-based PR risk prediction layer. Prerequisite for all supervised NN work: `pr_outcomes` populated with post-merge defect outcomes.

